@@TJvPanelOrientation
<TITLE TJvPanelOrientation type>
Summary
  Type used to specify the orientation of items in a TJvItemsPanel.
Description
  TJvPanelOrientation is used for the <LINK TJvItemsPanel.Orientation, Orientation> property to specify
  how items are displayed in the control.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvPanelOrientation.poHorizontal
  Items are displayed from left to right.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvPanelOrientation.poVertical
  Items are displayed from top to bottom.

